=====================================<br>
&quot;It (nuclear energy) is the only way to meet the greenhouse gas reduction goals of the EU and avoid increasing reliance on insecure energy imports,&quot; <br>
<br>
They are simply making an unsupported assertion, which is demonstratebly incorrect. (Just a tiny example for starters: Consistent UK ~offshore~ wind resources exceed the electrical demand for all of Europe)<br>
